The four puzzles present in the remake did not
exist in the original version. I believe that's
somewhat noticeable, because they don't have
the exact same vibe as most FNaFb content.
Zain added a nice amount of extra content in
other parts of the Complete Collection, so I
wanted new stuff in the Prelude as well. I hope
the puzzles are fun! I tried to make them easy.
This puzzle is directly taken from Off, an RPG
by Mortis Ghost also made in RPG Maker. It
follows the Batter, who's on a mission to purify
the world and free it from evil specters.
It's very different from the FNAFB games but I
absolutely recommend it. The plot is very
strange, though, so it won't be everyone's cup
of tea. An English translation is available.
